\c 10
\s Umbono kaDaniyeli emfuleni
\p
\v 1 Ngomnyaka wesithathu kaKoresi\x + 1.21.\x* inkosi yePerisiya ulutho lwembulelwa uDaniyeli\x + 6.28.\x*, obizo lakhe labizwa \add ngokuthi\add* nguBeliteshazari\x + 1.7.\x*. Njalo lolulutho lwaluliqiniso\x + 8.26.\x* mayelana lokulwisana okukhulu\x + Jobe 7.1.\x*\x + 10.14.\x*. Njalo waluqedisisa lolulutho, waba lokuqedisisa ngombono\x + 10.14.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Ngalezonsuku, mina Daniyeli ngangilila \add okw\add*amaviki amathathu agcweleyo\x + 10.13.\x*.
\v 3 Kangidlanga sinkwa esiloyisekayo, njalo kakuzanga nyama kumbe iwayini emlonyeni wami, futhi\x + Amos 6.6; Mat. 6.17.\x* kangizigcobanga ngitsho\x + 2 Lan. 28.15; Hlab. 23.5.\x*, kwaze kwagcwaliseka amaviki amathathu ezinsuku\x + 10.13.\x*.
\v 4 Kwathi ngosuku lwamatshumi amabili lane lwenyanga yokuqala\x + 10.1.\x*, mina ngiseceleni komfula omkhulu\x + Eks. 2.5.\x*, oyiHidekeli\x + Gen. 2.14.\x*;
\v 5 ngasengiphakamisa amehlo ami, ngabona, khangela-ke\x + Josh. 5.13.\x* umuntu othile\x + 12.6,7; 9.21.\x* egqoke ilembu elicolekileyo\x + Hez. 9.2.\x*, okhalo lwakhe lwalubhincwe\x + Isam. 1.13,15; 15.6.\x* ngegolide elicwengekileyo\x + Jobe 28.16.\x* leUfazi\x + Jer. 10.9.\x*.
\v 6 Lomzimba wakhe \w wawunjengebherule\w**\x + Hez. 1.16.\x*, lobuso bakhe\x + Hlu. 13.6.\x* babunjengesimo sombane\x + Mat. 28.3; Hez. 1.14; Isam. 1.16.\x*, lamehlo akhe njengezibane zomlilo\x + Isam. 1.14.\x*, lengalo zakhe lenyawo zakhe\x + Hez. 1.7.\x*\x + Isam. 1.15.\x* njengombala wethusi elikhazimulayo, lelizwi lamazwi akhe njengomsindo wexuku\x + Isam. 1.15.\x*\x + Isam. 19.6; Hez. 1.24.\x*.
\v 7 Yimi ngedwa uDaniyeli engabona lowombono\x + Seb. 9.7; 2 Kho. 6.17.\x*, ngoba abantu ababelami kabawubonanga umbono. Kodwa ukuqhuqha okukhulu kwabehlela, baze babaleka ukuze bacatshe\x + Seb. 9.7; 2 Kho. 6.17.\x*.
\v 8 Ngakho mina ngasala ngedwa, ngabona lumbono omkhulu, futhi kakusalanga mandla kimi\x + 7.28; Luka 1.12.\x*, lobuhle bami baguquka kimi baba yikonakala\x + Hos. 14.6 .\x*, kangisalelwanga ngamandla\x + 10.16; 11. 6; 1 Lan. 29.14.\x*.
\v 9 Ngasengisizwa ilizwi lamazwi akhe; njalo lapho ngisizwa ilizwi lamazwi akhe, mina ngehlelwa yibuthongo obukhulu ebusweni bami\x + 8.18.\x*, lobuso bami bungasemhlabathini\x + 8.18.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Khangela-ke, isandla sangithinta\x + 8.18.\x*, sangimisa ngithuthumela ngamadolo ami lempama zezandla zami\x + Hez. 2.9; Dan.10.16,18.\x*.
\v 11 Wasesithi kimi: Daniyeli, umuntu othandwe kakhulu, zwisisa amazwi engiwakhuluma kuwe, ume ngokuma kwakho\x + Hez. 2.1.\x*, ngoba khathesi ngithunywe kuwe\x + Heb. 1.14.\x*. Esekhulume lelilizwi kimi, ngema ngithuthumela\x + Ezra 10.9.\x*.
\v 12 Wasesithi kimi: Ungesabi, Daniyeli\x + 10.19; Isam. 1.17.\x*, ngoba kusukela osukwini lokuqala owabeka ngalo inhliziyo yakho ukuqedisisa\x + 9.3,4,22,23; Seb. 10.4.\x* lokuzithoba phambi kukaNkulunkulu wakho\x + Ezra 8.21; Levi 16.29.\x*, amazwi akho ezwakala, ngizile-ke mina ngenxa yamazwi akho\x + 9.3,4,22,23; Seb. 10.4.\x*.
\v 13 Kodwa isiphathamandla sombuso wamaPerisiya samelana lami\x + 10.20; Efe. 1.21; 2.2; 6.12; Josh. 5.14.\x* okwensuku ezingamatshumi amabili lanye\x + 10.2,3.\x*; kodwa khangela, uMikayeli omunye weziphathamandla zakuqala weza uku\add za\add*ngisiza\x + 10.21; 12.1; Juda 9; Isam. 12.7.\x*; mina ngasengisala khona ngasemakhosini ePerisiya.
\v 14 Khathesi ngizile ukuthi ngikwenze uqedisise okuzakwehlela abantu bakho ekucineni kwezinsuku\x + 2.28.\x*, ngoba umbono usengowezinsuku \add ezinengi\x + 8.26; 10.1; Hab. 2.3.\x*\add*.
\p
\v 15 Esekhulumile amazwi anje kimi, ngakhangelisa ubuso bami emhlabathini\x + 10.9; 8.18.\x*, ngaba yisimungulu\x + Hlab. 39.2,9.\x*.
\v 16 Khangela-ke, \add omunye\add* ofanana lomfanekiso\x + 8.15.\x* wamadodana abantu\x + Hlab. 58. 4.\x* wathinta indebe zami; ngasengivula umlomo wami, ngakhuluma\x + Hez. 2.9; Dan.10.16,18.\x*\x + Isa. 6.7.\x*, ngathi kulowo owayemi phambi kwami: Nkosi yami, ngenxa yombono izinsizi zami \add se\add*ziphendukele phezu kwami, kangaba lamandla\x + 7.28; Luka 1.12.\x*\x + 10.16; 11.6; 1 Lan. 29.14.\x*.
\v 17 Ngoba inceku yale inkosi yami ingaba lakho ukukhuluma njani lale inkosi yami? Mayelana lami, kusukela ngalesosikhathi kakusalanga mandla kimi, lokuphefumula kwakungasekho kimi.
\p
\v 18 Wasebuya wangithinta\x + Hez. 2.9; Dan.10.16,18.\x* onjengomfanekiso womuntu, wangiqinisa\x + 8.15.\x*.
\v 19 Wasesithi: Ungesabi, muntu othandiweyo kakhulu\x + 10.11.\x*; ukuthula kakube kuwe\x + Hlu. 6.23; Gen. 43.23; Dan.10.12.\x*, qina, yebo, qina\x + Dute. 31.7,23.\x*. Kwathi esekhulume lami, ngaqiniswa, ngathi: Kayikhulume inkosi yami, ngoba ungiqinisile.
\v 20 Wasesithi: Uyazi yini ukuthi ngizeleni kuwe? Khathesi-ke ngizabuyela uku\add za\add*kulwa lesiphathamandla sePerisiya\x + 10.13.\x*; lalapho \add se\add*ngiphumile, khangela-ke, isiphathamandla seGirisi sizafika\x + 8.21.\x*.
\v 21 Kodwa ngizakutshela lokho okubhaliweyo embhalweni\x + 12.1,4.\x* weqiniso\x + 11.2.\x*; njalo kakho loyedwa obambisana lami kulezizinto, ngaphandle kukaMikayeli isiphathamandla senu\x + 10.13.\x*.